&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To move the Y axis to the right side, set &lt;a href=&quot;http://api.highcharts.com#yAxis.opposite&quot;&gt;yAxis.opposite&lt;/a&gt; to true.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To reverse the X axis, set &lt;a href=&quot;http://api.highcharts.com#xAxis.reversed&quot;&gt;xAxis.reversed&lt;/a&gt; to true.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Live demo&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;See a &lt;a href=&quot;http://jsfiddle.net/highcharts/buYCZ/&quot;&gt;live Arabic chart&lt;/a&gt; demo.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
